---
import LessonShell from '../components/LessonShell.astro';
import IrregularVerbTrainer from '../components/IrregularVerbTrainer.jsx';

export const frontmatter = {
  title: "Lektion 3｜不規則動詞",
  description: "整理德語強變化與不規則動詞的三態、haben/sein、情態動詞與錯誤紀錄。",
  category: "文法練習",
  tags: ["A1-C1", "不規則動詞", "Perfekt", "Modalverben", "語音"],
  order: 3,
  level: "A1-C1",
  estimatedMinutes: 20,
  theme: "violet"
};
---

<LessonShell frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <IrregularVerbTrainer client:load />
  </div>

  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>背不規則動詞時，建議一起記 Infinitiv、Präteritum、Perfekt 三態，而不是分開記。</span>
  </li>
  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>同時注意 Perfekt 用 haben 還是 sein，這是實際使用時最容易錯的地方之一。</span>
  </li>
  <li slot="tips" class="flex items-start gap-2">
    <span class="text-current opacity-70 mt-0.5">•</span>
    <span>先把高頻動詞練熟，再慢慢擴充到較少見的變化，記憶會穩很多。</span>
  </li>
</LessonShell>
